data.description: Great N. Kihei 4 bedroom 3 bath, 1,863 sqft. home. Located on the single street subdivision of Ho’oiki Place in Kenolio Mauka. The value is having two ensuite primary bedrooms, one on each floor. The kitchen, living room, dining area, laundry room, and one primary bedroom (which includes its own entrance) is on the ground floor and the other ensuite bedroom, with an additional two bedrooms and a full bath is upstairs. There is a 2 car garage, a large 119 gallon solar hot water heater, laminate and tile floors, visitor parking and a private park towards the back of the culdesac. Property will be sold AS IS. A VA mortgage for part of the purchase may possibly be assumable? (Ask your VA lender). Kenolio Mauka is close to wonderful South Maui beaches, schools, and shopping.
